Wed Jul 08 05:12:08 UTC 2026 - Johannes Kastl <opensuse_buildservice@ojkastl.de>

- Update to version 1.23.0:
  * added
    - Code viewer for large code blocks
    - Support for mermaid charts in README files
    - Support for markdown in MOTD banner
    - Deprecated annotation in Tekton packages
    - Allow overriding db password in migrate script
    - Option to set tolerations (chart)
    - Option to set common labels (chart)
    - Option to set extra volumes and env vars in db-migrator
      (chart)
  * changed
    - Some improvements to OCI package (including signature
      detection)
    - Improve security alerts notifications
    - Improve union type default handling in values schema viewer
    - Update FAQ
    - Bump Alpine to 3.24.1
    - Bump Go to 1.26.4
    - Bump Trivy to 0.69.3
    - Upgrade backend and frontend dependencies
  * fixed
    - Do not strip underscores from changes descriptions
    - Some issues in router
    - Some issues caused by lazy loaded routes
    - Issue rendering banner on Safari 26.4
    - Chart template rendering in the web UI
    - Repository opt-out search highlighting error

